            <h2>Terms &amp; Conditions</h2>
            <h3 id="01">Introduction</h3>
            <p>Welcome, and thank you for visiting the My Ecommerce website at myecommerce.pornhub.gov (hereinafter this/the “<em>Website</em>”). This Website is operated by Armenia My Ecommerce Co., Ltd. (hereinafter “<em>My Ecommerce</em>”) a Armenian incorporated company located in Yerevan, Armenia.</p>
