                <p>All orders are subject to acceptance and availability; products in your shopping bag are not held or reserved and may be purchased by other customers.</p>
                <p>Once your order has been submitted to us by clicking “Order confirmation”, you will receive an e-mail acknowledging the details of your order (an “Order Acknowledgement E-mail”).
