                </ol>
                <p>If there are any problems with any of the requirements above, we will not be able to accept your order and you will be notified via e-mail. If all of the requirements are met, we will send you an e-mail confirming the acceptance of your order (an “Order Acceptance E-mail”).</p>
                <p>Since we operate Monday through Friday and are closed on Saturdays, Sundays, and Armenian National holidays, orders submitted on Friday evening, Saturday, or Sunday (based on Armenia
