                <p>Following the acceptance of your order, the shipping process will start. We will carefully package the products and prepare documentation for shipping. After the package is prepared, it will be shipped to you via the shipping company. Subsequently you will receive an e-mail confirming (an “Order Completion E-mail”) that your order has been completed and the package has
