                After your package has been dispatched, the process of cancelling your order will be classed as a Return. Please refer to the Returns process section for details. Please be advised that fees will be incurred in cancelling an order once it is classed as a Return.</p>
                <h3 id="02">Shipping</h3>
                <p>My Ecommerce prides itself on offering the highest quality products and fulfilling your orders accurately. All of our products are inspected prior to shipment so as to guarantee that they meet our quality standards.<br />
                    All orders are shipped from My Ecommerce in Yerevan, Armenia. We operate Monday through Friday and are closed on Saturdays, Sundays, and Armenian National holidays. Orders submitted on
