                <p>If you decide to refuse any shipments from My Ecommerce for any reasons not clearly attributable to My Ecommerce, you will be held responsible for the original shipping charges, duties, taxes and/or customs charges that are or have been incurred by the package (on both the original and return shipments), and the fees for returning the package to My Ecommerce. These costs will
                be deducted from any eventual refund.</p>
                <h3 id="03">Order tracking</h3>
                <p>All orders can be tracked during shipment and we will notify you of the tracking number and other necessary information as soon as it is available to us.<br />
