            <h4 id="04-06">Refunds</h4>
            <p>Every effort will be made to ensure a prompt refund to you with e-mail notifications from the returns process. When your returned products are delivered back to us, you will receive a
                confirmation e-mail. Please allow up to 2 business days for the full inspection and review of the condition of the returned products. If we have any questions regarding your returns, we will
