            <p>Please allow up to approximately 6 weeks from the time we have confirmed the fulfilment of the conditions of returns for the refund to be credited back to your account. Refunds will be
            made to PayPal account used to make the original purchase.</p>
            <h3 id="05">Product pricing and fees</h3>
            <p>The list price of each product is set and fixed in Armenian Dram (AMD) exclusive of Armenian consumption tax and any shipping and handling fees or any other fees.
            The list price represents purely the price of the product in Armenia, prices that are very competitive compared to other Armenian domestic vendors for the same quality product.</p>
            <p>Shipping and handling fees are charged separately after you enter into payment phase, and it is the only fee that we charge besides the list price. (Consumption tax is charged when
            purchased within Armenia.)</p>
            <p>For international purchases all items are Armenian DUTY  FREE, however please be on notice that you are liable for all customs duties and taxes levied by the destination country. Payment of such duties and taxes may be necessary
            upon delivery. Charges to your PayPal account made by My Ecommerce are totally exclusive of such duties and taxes. In no circumstance will we charge customs duties or taxes to your PayPal.</p>
            <h4 id="05-01">Pricing in your local currency guide only</h4>
            <p>For international purchases, prices are displayed in the currency based on the currency chosen by you. These local currency prices are calculated based on the actual price in JPY using a
                foreign currency exchange rate service (updated daily), such prices may fluctuate due to exchange rate fluctuations. Please note that prices displayed in your local currency are to be used as a guide only,
                the final price of the product charged to you in your local currency is solely dependent on your credit/debit card provider along with PayPal’s foreign exchange rates and polices. Please be aware
