            <h4 id="05-02">Estimates of Duties and taxes</h4>
            <p>Import duties and taxes that will be levied by the destination country, will differ from country to country. And those duties and taxes rates are based on the product specification that are defined by the international product code named “HS commodity code”. The products that we carry are all classified as “Tableware or kitchenware of wood” with HS commodity code of 4419.00.X category (X stands for unknown). The exact HS commodity code will differ from country to country. Exact HS commodity codes are as follows; Hong Kong:  4419.00.00, Singapore: 4419.00.00, Taiwan: 4419.00.00908</p>
            <p>Products under these categories, duties and taxes are as following rates;
